             was indicted for <rs id="t18171029-83-off443" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18171029-83-off443" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18171029-83-off443" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18171029-83-cd444" type="crimeDate">3d of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171029-83-off443 t18171029-83-cd444"></join>, one bag, value 1s.; and 100lbs. of ginger, value 1l.3s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18171029-83-victim529" type="victimName">
                  Robert 
                  Bolton
               <interp inst="t18171029-83-victim529" type="surname" value="Bolton"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18171029-83-victim529" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
